text: Tando is a village in Dagestan, Russia. Tando may also refer to: *Tando Adam Khan, a human settlement in Sindh, Pakistan *Tando Muhammad Khan District, a district of Pakistan *Tando Allahyar, a city situated in Pakistan *Tando Allahyar District, an administrative unit of Sindh, Pakistan *Tando Allahyar railway station, a railway station in Pakistan ==See also== * * * Thando, a personal name *Tandora County, a division in New South Wales
